{"type":"answer","id":9368,"parentType":"question","parentId":2122,"uid":1393,"contents":"這邊有個女的，她被國寶弄了一次之後就被氣得上吊自殺了。<br>\n<br>\n我希望大家引以為戒，自殺只會讓魔鬼們笑得更猖狂。因為他們甚至不必揮動鐮刀而使韭菜自然倒下。<br>\n<br>\n大家要記住，只有活著才能繼續和魔鬼們作對，死了就一文不值了！<br>\n<br>\n在這兒洗地說此事和共產黨無關的也省省，看看人家親歷者是怎麼說的。<br>\n<br>\n而且這事的關鍵是只立案，不調查。甚至第一家被凍結資金的機構，還是被新加坡政府主動幫忙凍結的，而且只凍結了新加坡境內銀行的錢。<br>\n<br>\n更關鍵的是：不調查不凍結也就算了，還把受害者列為了和法輪功一樣級別的“非法組織成員”，進行鎮壓法輪功級別的維穩，可是政府全然忘記了自己是怎麼在2015年大力支持發展p2p的，按政府的邏輯政府自己都是“非法組織”了。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180907/1536316906569530.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180907/1536316906569530.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180907/1536316906569530.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180907/1536316916867029.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180907/1536316916867029.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180907/1536316916867029.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180907/1536316923429892.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180907/1536316923429892.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180907/1536316923429892.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180907/1536316930828493.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180907/1536316930828493.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180907/1536316930828493.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2018-09-07","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}